{"tid":1808331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人再次揚威海外！在德國「盜版產品大獎」中我國廠商包攬所有獎項","createTime":"2020-01-02T09:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T10:31:48.000Z","uid":154054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1236d87109636e5d197e077e0adbf55a546eb970","tid":1808331,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"2019 翻版產品大獎出爐 中國包攬所有獎項揚威國際<br />\n發佈時間<br />\n19 小時前<br />\n德國 Plagiarius 每年都會公佈一個名爲「金鼻子剽竊獎（Plagiarius Awarding）」的獎項，「表揚」年內最突出的翻版產品，他們最近就公佈了 2019 年的得獎名單，全部由中國企業包辦，揚威國際。<br />\n今年的大獎總共有 10 個得獎產品，其中冠軍是由中國寧波工業自動化公司推出的角座閥，其整個產品線都是抄襲自德國 B&uuml;rkert Werke 公司的「Type 2000」，除了產品設計，就連國際商標都完整照抄過去，以假亂真程度令人咋舌。<br />\n亞軍是恒亨玩具廠推出的玩具鏟泥車，抄襲德國 BRUDER Spielwaren 的產品「Liebherr Articulated Road Loader」，不論設計、生產技術和各部分比例都是完整抄襲並縮小一個尺碼，但使用的原料和做功都較差。德國廠商已經與中國玩具公司庭外和解並獲得賠償。<br />\n季軍由浙江柯藍工貿有限公司的鑄鐵鍋奪得，其抄襲對象是德國 ZWILLING J.A. Henckels AG 的 Staub Cocotte 鑄鐵鍋，除了產品上的商標之外完全 1:1 照抄，不過山寨版本並不是鑄鐵材質，而是較廉價的鋁質，其成本只是本身的十分之一。<br />\n除了冠亞季軍之外，另外也有 6 個「優異獎」及 1 個「特別獎」。<br />\n來源：Plagiarius<br />\n所有盜版及正版品對比照片請看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/01/plagiarius-award-2019/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F01%2Fplagiarius-award-2019%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1c11f98f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/01/plagiarius-award-2019/fun-tech/</a><br />\n所有照片左邊為正版，右邊為盜版。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3cfed4db5310dac24fa569985f32839d9790f3","tid":1808331,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的蟈"},{"pid":"c539e3f2974f4849d6d5f41b31e4d61064b22e09","tid":1808331,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:58:30.000Z","msg":"鬼國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbf3d0aeb3c7dc96d6685c399a75bebcf06cf45","tid":1808331,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"咁德國佬肯反共未？"},{"pid":"3010690ffb60e9250ce30ea70dc107f6a8cc3e67","tid":1808331,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbf3d0aeb3c7dc96d6685c399a75bebcf06cf45","tid":1808331,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"咁德國佬肯反共未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"識一個德國佬，用緊華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecc638e319c65d484cc63ec8e1f5041872aac81","tid":1808331,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"共匪！！"}]}